Excellent quality, for those that are wondering this includes 4 remixes of the song, as well as the original mix.

1. Chase & Status - Let You Go
2. Chase & Status - Let You Go (Brookes Brothers remix)
3. Chase & Status - Let You Go (VIP Mix)
4. Chase & Status - Let You Go (Feed Me Remix)
5. Chase & Status - Let You Go (Nero Remix)
